snippet.title: Catrophy Trail - Early Access Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Catrophy Trail is a light-hearted physics adventure game where you use teamwork and wits to solve physics-based puzzles, gather valuable loot, and collect gear for future expeditions.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2224060/Catrophy_Trail/
